      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery flows.",
      "rationale": "The solver has been verified against the Taylor-Green vortex and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Published verification reports confirm numerical correctness of the incompressible Navier-Stokes implementation used in this study."
    },
