      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenarios span the operating envelope of the COU including worst-case flow-speed combinations.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted at the boundary and interior of the 5-point operating envelope. The worst-case hemolysis operating point identified by CFD was included in the validation set, confirming that the model correctly identifies the extremum."
