      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles, rotational speed, fluid density, and viscosity are fully documented with literature sources. Uncertainty ranges were specified for blood viscosity (±8%) and inlet flow rate (±3%) and propagated through the UQ analysis. The UQ report notes that a formal sensitivity analysis ranking input drivers is planned for the next revision cycle but was not completed prior to this submission."
    },
