    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo propagation confirms output uncertainty within acceptable bounds for the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The model is credible for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions.",
